PREHEAT oven to broil. PREPARE Garlic Chicken according to package instructions, adding chiles and lime juice. Wrap tortillas in damp towel; microwave on high 40 to 50 seconds or until warm. FOR EACH BURRTIO: spoon one eighth chicken mixture across center of tortilla. Top filling with 1/4 cup cheese and 2 tablespoons salsa. Fold in both sides. Place burrito folded side down on broiler-safe pan or platter. Repeat. BROIL 1 minute or until browned. Serve with remaining salsa and lime wedges.